I"4<ol>
  <li>Save <code class="highlighter-rouge">iptables</code> rules:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>iptables-save <span class="o">&gt;</span> /etc/iptables.conf
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/network/interfaces</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>...
iface eth0 inet dhcp
  pre-up iptables-restore &lt; /etc/iptables.conf
...
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

